data.description: Beautiful country home built in 1860 and was completely renovated in 2017. It has a new leach field and septic. Furnace, central air, and water heater all new in 2017. Offers 2 possibly 3 bedrooms or office space. Laundry room on the second floor with butcher block counter. Original hardwood floor in the living room, dining room and hallway. Strand bamboo in the rest of the house.  Also, offers a mud room and a storm cellar.  The two-car garage has wood fireplace.
